reviews.text: Food quality in lunch sets is good. Price for lunch sets is acceptable, ranging from about $100 - $200. Good and efficient services from waiters/ waitresses.

Very nice japanese restaurant. Good service and didnt need to wait for long. 
Menu has sashimi/sushi/rolls, Teppayaki, yakimono, sukiyaki etc. Lots to choose from. 

We had the #1203 Assorted Sashimi and Sushi set, #505 Angus Beef rice (in hot pot) and some kind of cold noodles. The angus beef was very good and came with a small miso soup as well.
Pricey in terms of food quality, does not seem like authentic japanese food in general
Good value for the quality of food.
Delicious Japanese food, friendly service, and exceptional value for money.

result.name: 市川日本料理

reviews.text: Food quality in lunch sets is good. Price for lunch sets is acceptable, ranging from about $100 - $200. Good and efficient services from waiters/ waitresses.

Very nice japanese restaurant. Good service and didnt need to wait for long. 
Menu has sashimi/sushi/rolls, Teppayaki, yakimono, sukiyaki etc. Lots to choose from. 

We had the #1203 Assorted Sashimi and Sushi set, #505 Angus Beef rice (in hot pot) and some kind of cold noodles. The angus beef was very good and came with a small miso soup as well.
服務良好，環境舒適，食物：鐵板燒師傅唔夠功夫，“貴價壽司”師傅合格，“平價壽司”徒弟不合格。其它食物還可以。平平無奇，一般貨色，收費略高。

食物質素仍然保持水準👍
服務態度仍然有善有禮👍
연어회 상태가 좋았고, 특히 소프트쉘크랩 튀김이 맛있어습니다. 샤브샤브도 깔끔한 국물맛에 담백했습니다.  아래 후기와 다르게 저는 전반적으로 괜찮았던 것 같습니다. 특히, 텟판야키를 하는 요리부와 스시요리부 섹션이 나눠져있어서 위생적으로 보였습니다. 시티플라자 안에서는 아시안 푸드 중에 괜찮은 집이라고 생각합니다.
